docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n <div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Unerwünscht:</strong> Dieses Feature wurde aus den Webstandards entfernt. Obwohl manche Browser es immer noch unterstützen, wird es zukünftig wegfallen. Es sollte daher nicht mehr in alten oder neuen Projekten verwendet werden. Webseiten oder Webapps, die es benutzen, funktionieren möglicherweise irgendwann nicht mehr korrekt.</p></div></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"übersicht","title":"Übersicht","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das HTML Center Element (<code>&lt;center&gt;</code>) ist ein <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements\" title=\"HTML/Block-level_elements\">Block-Level Element</a>, welches Paragraphen oder andere Block-Level Elemente und Inline Elemente enthalten kann. Der gesamte Inhalt des Elements wird horizontal zentriert, innerhalb des übergeordneten Elements (normalerweise das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> Element). Dieses Element ist in HTML 4 (und XHTML 1) veraltet und wird nicht mehr angewendet, zu Gunsten der <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/text-align\"><code>text-align</code></a> Eigenschaft, welche auf <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> Elemente oder individuell auf <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> Elemente angewendet werden kann.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_schnittstelle","title":"DOM Schnittstelle","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Schnittstelle.</p>\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n <p><strong>Implementierungs Anmerkung:</strong> Bis einschließlich Gecko 1.9.2, implementiert Firefox die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Schnittstelle für dieses Element.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_1","title":"Beispiel 1","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dieser Text wird zentriert.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Ebenso dieser Paragraph.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_2","title":"Beispiel 2 (CSS Alternative)","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dieser Text wird zentriert.\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Ebenso dieser Paragraph.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_3","title":"Beispiel 3 (CSS alternative)","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>center</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dieser Text wird zentriert.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\nEbenso dieser Paragraph.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Anmerkung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Bei Zuweisung der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/text-align\"><code>text-align</code></a><code>:center</code> Eigenschaft zu einem&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> oder <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> Element, wird der <em>Inhalt</em> des Elements zentriert, während dessen Größe unverändert bleibt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/text-align\"><code>text-align</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"sect4\">\n </div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"übersicht"},{"text":"DOM Schnittstelle","id":"dom_schnittstelle"},{"text":"Beispiel 1","id":"example_1"},{"text":"Beispiel 2 (CSS Alternative)","id":"example_2"},{"text":"Beispiel 3 (CSS alternative)","id":"example_3"},{"text":"Anmerkung","id":"notes"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML Center Element (<center>) ist ein Block-Level Element, welches Paragraphen oder andere Block-Level Elemente und Inline Elemente enthalten kann. Der gesamte Inhalt des Elements wird horizontal zentriert, innerhalb des übergeordneten Elements (normalerweise das <body> Element). Dieses Element ist in HTML 4 (und XHTML 1) veraltet und wird nicht mehr angewendet, zu Gunsten der CSS text-align Eigenschaft, welche auf <div> Elemente oder individuell auf <p> Elemente angewendet werden kann.","popularity":0.0013,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<center>: The Centered Text element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<center> (obsoleto)","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<center> : l'élément de texte centré","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<center>: 文字列の中央揃え要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<center>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"center","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<center>: O elemento de texto centralizado (obsoleto)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<center>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/center","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/center/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/center","title":"<center>"}],"pageTitle":"<center> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}